metadata.description: BlockFriends NFT merges the nostalgia of early cartoons with new age vibrant street art influences, creating a fusion of unique, edgy, and colorful NFTs on the Ethereum Blockchain. BlockFriends NFT is a collection of 105 NFTs that are all 1/1 and entirely hand crafted for your enjoyment. The artist has created a series of art for those who appreciate the old school meets new school art movement on the blockchain.unique digital collectibles living on the Ethereum blockchain. Holders receive special giveaways, and access to an exclusive community within the metaverse. Visit www.metagreys.io for more details.
